         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Midnight, 30/9/95 ¶  ¶ It was very kind of you, dear Chev Dejardin to offer your friendly influence for the passage of my case of the dwarf Grasstree (Xanthorrhoea minor) to the jardin des plantes. ¶ ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">95.09.30</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Léon Dejardin</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Carton no. 16, Melbourne, consulat, Serie A, Centre des Archives Diplomatiques, Nantes.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>For a printed version of this letter, see Home &amp; Maroske (1997), p. 48.</p>
               </note>Midnight, 30/9/95</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It was very kind of you, dear Chev Dejardin to offer your friendly influence for the passage of my case of the dwarf Grasstree (<name key="Xanthorrhoea%20minor">Xanthorrhoea minor</name>) to the jardin des plantes.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to L. Dejardin, 25 September 1895.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The case arrived this afternoon; so I thought to send it at once straight on the same cart to Port Melbourne, where the Captain of the Messageries maritimes kindly took it. Thus it will be in Paris before severe frosts commence.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I hope, the Capt. of next months steamer will take a case of minerals to the Musée d'histoire naturelle also. Thanking you for all your friendliness</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">your Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Xanthorrhoea%20minor">Xanthorrhoea minor</name>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
